org.osgi.cdi.api.extension.events
Class AbstractServiceEvent

java.lang.Object
  org.osgi.cdi.api.extension.events.AbstractServiceEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
ServiceArrival, ServiceChanged, ServiceDeparture
public abstract class AbstractServiceEvent
extends Object

Represents all the CDI-OSGi service events as a superclass.

Provides a way to listen all service events in a single method. Allows to retrieve both original event type as a BundleEventType and the firing service informations.

Author:
Mathieu ANCELIN - SERLI (mathieu.ancelin@serli.com), Matthieu CLOCHARD - SERLI (matthieu.clochard@serli.com)
